title: FL Studio 12.5.0.58 (Incl. The Only Working Registration Key)
description:
After digging deep into the dark web forums and underground communities I nearly found a working way of registration for the newest version of FL Studio which isn't cracked by any team yet.


- Disable your fuckin' AV
- Install like always
- Don't run FL.exe! 
- Run "Patch.exe" as admin and click Patch
- Seed
- Seed again
- Seed and seed 
- Seed till you bleed
- Seed till the cops break your door
- Seed till you die
- Enjoy! ;) 


Now I strongly recommend you to block all FL exe files (32, 64, scaled, memory compatible) from accessing the internet via your Windows firewall or using any other firewall programs. I personally like to use avast! Firewall which comes with the Premiere edition of avast!. 
And if you don't block FL from accessing the internet chances are too damn high that your license will be banned and your machine ID will be blacklisted in Image-Line servers so you might not be able to use the method I provide again or maybe never ever. Remember to block FL from accessing the internet using a firewall. BLOCK ALL THE EXE FILES!
This is not a final solution for your first world problem.. Just wait till R2R or one of those legends rise and "FiKs da Bugzz" in FL 12.5 ;)



Ny2rogen/Team PH4T0G3N
